BNP Paribas Won’t Seek Any Large Staff Reductions Globally, CEO Prot Says

-- B y   F a b i o   B e n e d e t t i - V a l e n t i n i   a n d   C a r o l i n e   C o n n a n
-- 
2011-08-02T05:48:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-02/bnp-paribas-won-t-seek-any-large-staff-reductions-globally-ceo-prot-says.html
BNP Paribas (BNP)  SA won’t seek any large
staff cuts globally and might look to “some local” adjustments
in its workforce, Chief Executive Officer  Baudouin Prot  said in
an interview with Bloomberg Television in Paris.  “We might have to update and make some local adaptations
but I don’t see the need for big staff reduction” at BNP
Paribas, Prot said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Fabio Benedetti-Valentini at 
 fabiobv@bloomberg.net  